{
  "stem": "21786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was divided then, depending, again, on the number of the sick persons and the number-- and the kind of mood of whoever was cutting it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When did you begin working in the hospital?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I began working about six weeks after-- after we arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe months-- six weeks after I arrived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, in [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] June 6, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 1944-- no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What am I saying?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They got off in-- in March 6, 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "An order came that the original transport, which came there, the 5,000 people from Theresienstadt, they will be transferred to a different camp called, Heydebreck, H-E-Y-D-E-B-R-E-C-K.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every truck-- such a move of populace in any camp, everybody knows that it probably is deadly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the transport was supposed to leave on the 6 of March.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On 6 of March, each and every block was completely blocked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were special kind of squadron of SS men was put into the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were several hundred SS men with dogs and with guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were transferred.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These 5,000 people they transferred to the camp A, neighboring to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Prepared for transportation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By the same time, we had such a kind-- such kind there was a certain resistance in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from camp to camp went a signal that the special commando which handled-- handles the gas chambers and crematoria is called 'the full attention.' And at the same time, there is a special amount of SS men guarding the truck toward-- towards the-- towards the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And during the night, simply, the blocks were closed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was absolute [GERMAN], closure of the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we heard terrible noises, and terrible beating, and terrible screams.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were loading them into trucks naked.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
